    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double VANOS for a linear power band up to its 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain consists of a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox paired with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to mitigate common chassis fatigue. It rides on a refined suspension setup with upgraded bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear geometry perform exactly as intended. Mechanically sound with excellent compression across all cylinders, this M3 is a driver-focused example that prioritizes performance and structural integrity.",
