      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2018 Audi Q5 Premium Plus that perfectly balances luxury and utility. This vehicle has been garage-kept and serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive maintenance log available for your review. The exterior shines in its original Moonlight Blue Metallic paint; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway driving, the body remains straight and free of any significant dings or scratches. Inside, the Atlas Beige leather interior is in excellent shape, showing only slight softening on the driver's seat bolster and no tears or stains. All technological features\u2014including the Audi Virtual Cockpit, panoramic sunroof, and Bang & Olufsen 3D sound system\u2014function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in top form: the 2.0T engine pulls smoothly, the Quattro AWD system provides confident handling, and a fresh set of Michelin Pilot Sport All-Season tires was installed just 5,000 miles ago. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner who appreciates a car that has been treated with genuine care and professional attention.",
